Package databaseData

Class IntegerPost

java.lang.Object
databaseData.Post
databaseData.IntegerPost
public class IntegerPost extends Post
The IntegerPost class represents an integer. It is used to help detect when things have been loaded in from Firebase or once something has been uploaded to Firebase.
